label: AB12C_cP14_221_a_h_b-001
title: Predicted High-Pressure YCaH$_{12}$ Structure
comments:
This structure was determined by {\em ab initio} methods and is predicted to be stable in the pressure range 180-257GPa, with $T_{c} = 230$K at 180GPa.  We show the predicted structure at 200GPa. 
 The ICSD entry is from the calculations of (Liang, 2019).
